				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "## API Chain for LOB App Binaries\n\nThe Graph API exposes the download URL for LOB app binaries through a 4-step chain:\n\n1. **List apps**: `GET /deviceAppManagement/mobileApps` — filter for LOB types ({{gtMethod:IntuneMobileApp>>#isLobApp}})\n2. **Content versions**: `GET .../mobileApps/{id}/{lobType}/contentVersions`\n3. **Content files**: `GET .../contentVersions/{versionId}/files`\n4. **Storage URI**: The {{gtClass:IntuneContentFile}} has `azureStorageUri` — a time-limited SAS URL to Azure Blob Storage\n\nThe convenience method {{gtMethod:IntuneGraphClient>>#storageUriForApp:}} walks the full chain in one call."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-03-21T17:10:32.02011-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-03-21T17:10:32.02011-04:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "A4qP6mmiSxOYOf9MhG4sOg=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "## Getting the Storage URI for a LOB App"
			},
			{
				"__type" : "pharoSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-03-21T17:10:37.01452-04:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-03-21T17:22:45.227668-04:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "b3IF8g/nSCW2czFpbDBgiw=="
				},
				"code" : "\"Get the Azure Blob SAS URL for a LOB app\"\nclient := IntuneGraphClient new\n\ttenantId: 'your-tenant-id';\n\tclientId: 'your-client-id';\n\tclientSecret: 'your-client-secret'.\nlobApps := client lobApps.\nlobApps items ifNotEmpty: [ :apps |\n\tclient storageUriForApp: apps first ]."
			},
