				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "## Domain Model\n\n- {{gtClass:IntuneMobileApp}} / {{gtClass:IntuneMobileApps}} — Mobile apps from Intune (store + LOB)\n- {{gtClass:IntuneContentVersion}} / {{gtClass:IntuneContentVersions}} — Content versions for a LOB app\n- {{gtClass:IntuneContentFile}} / {{gtClass:IntuneContentFiles}} — Content files with Azure Storage SAS URIs\n\nAll entity classes extend {{gtClass:IntuneDataEntity}} and group classes extend {{gtClass:IntuneDataGroup}}, reusing the existing serialization and `TGtGroupWithItems` patterns from the Microsoft package."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
