					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "pwhRs1f3Sw2RBoXTo9K5EQ=="
				},
				"code" : "\"Walk the chain step by step: app → versions → files → file detail with SAS URI\"\nclient := IntuneGraphClient new\n\ttenantId: 'your-tenant-id';\n\tclientId: 'your-client-id';\n\tclientSecret: 'your-client-secret'.\napp := client lobApps items first.\nversions := app contentVersions.\nfiles := versions items last files.\nfile := files items first fetchDetails.\nfile."
			},
